A:/> C:
C:/> 
C:/> debug.app
NostOS Debug
Type ? for help
-
-?
B               List breakpoints
B addr          Set breakpoint
BC addr|*       Clear breakpoint(s)
D [addr]        Dump memory
E addr bb [..]  Enter bytes
F start end bb  Fill memory
G [addr]        Go (run)
I port          Input port
L file [addr]   Load program
O port bb       Output port
P               Proceed (step over)
Q               Quit
R               Register dump
R reg=val       Modify register
T               Trace (step into)
U [addr]        Unassemble
